The fasthtml.xt Namespace
Some people prefer to write code using namespaces while adhering to PEP8. If that’s a preference, projects can be coded using the fasthtml.xt namespace.

from fasthtml import xt

xt.Ul(
    xt.Li("one"),
    xt.Li("two"),
    xt.Li("three")
)

